Package nl.han.ica.yaeger.engine.scenes

Interface YaegerScene

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Clearable, Configurable, Destroyable, Initializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DynamicScene, StaticScene
    public interface YaegerScene
extends Destroyable, Initializable, Configurable, Clearable
    A YaegerScene encapsulates a scene or level from a Yaeger Game.
